a href="https://x.com/paulogoncalvs" aria-label="X (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link"><svg aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-x" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="fill-current"><use href="/assets/img/sprite.svg#sprite-x"></use></svg></a></div><div class="relative inline-block"><a href="https://github.com/paulogoncalvs" aria-label="GitHub (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link"><svg aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-github" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="fill-current"><use href="/assets/img/sprite.svg#sprite-github"></use></svg></a></div><div class="relative inline-block"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulogoncalvs" aria-label="LinkedIn (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link"><svg aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-linkedin" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="fill-current"><use href="/assets/img/sprite.svg#sprite-linkedin"></use></svg></a></div></div></div></aside><main class="flex flex-1 flex-col space-y-16 text-center"><section class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-14 px-6 pt-16"><h1><span style="--delay:100ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down">PAULO GONÇALVES</span><span style="--delay:200ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down">Front-End Engineer</span></h1><div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-14 sm:flex-row sm:space-y-0"><div style="--delay:300ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down shrink-0"><img alt="portrait of Paulo Gonçalves" width="240" height="240" src="/assets/img/paulo-goncalves-240.CPwabXJs.jpeg" srcset="/assets/img/paulo-goncalves-240.CPwabXJs.jpeg 1x, /assets/img/paulo-goncalves-400.DXr5Bgs3.jpeg 2x" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 240px, 240px" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="transition-all duration-500 ease-out motion-reduce:transition-none opacity-100 rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/30 shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.75),0_0_9px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2),0_3px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]"></div><div style="--delay:400ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down max-w-sm text-left text-sm sm:max-w-lg sm:pl-14 sm:text-base"><p>Native of Vila Nova de Gaia, Porto, Portugal.<br><br>With more than 20 years of professional experience, I am currently a <strong>Principal Front-End Engineer</strong> at <strong>Porto Tech Center - Jumia</strong>, focused on building scalable, high-performance web applications.<br><br>I lead front-end architecture, define technical direction, and promote best practices while leveraging modern frameworks and tooling.<br><br>Driven by performance and user experience, I collaborate across teams to deliver robust, user-centric solutions and tackle complex engineering challenges.</p></div></div></section><section class="flex flex-col items-center border-t border-white/80 bg-white/5 px-6 py-16 text-center dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-zinc-900/15"><div class="w-full max-w-sm text-left sm:max-w-xl"><h2 style="--delay:200ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down mb-12">Professional Experience</h2><div style="--delay:200ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div style="--delay:0ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="my-11 last:mb-0"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">Jumia Porto Tech Center</h3><p class="mb-3 text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">11 years 3 months</p><div class="relative ml-3"><span class="absolute top-3 bottom-0 -left-0.5 w-2 -translate-x-1/3 rounded bg-stone-300/60 dark:bg-white/5"></span><div class="space-y-4"><div style="--delay:0ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-black dark:border-zinc-500 dark:bg-white"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Principal Front-End Engineer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Oct 2022  Present · 3 years 4 months</p></div></div><div style="--delay:15ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Engineering Manager / Lead Front-End Engineer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Sep 2021  Oct 2022 · 1 year 2 months</p></div></div><div style="--delay:30ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Lead Front-End Engineer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Jun 2020  Aug 2021 · 1 year 3 months</p></div></div><div style="--delay:44.99999999999999ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Web Engineer (Senior Front-End Engineer)</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Apr 2016  Jun 2020 · 4 years 3 months</p></div></div><div style="--delay:60ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Senior Front-End Developer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Nov 2014  Apr 2016 · 1 year 6 months</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="--delay:20ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="my-11 last:mb-0"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">Rocket Internet GmbH</h3><p class="mb-3 text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">2 years 6 months</p><div class="relative ml-3"><span class="absolute top-3 bottom-0 -left-0.5 w-2 -translate-x-1/3 rounded bg-stone-300/60 dark:bg-white/5"></span><div class="space-y-4"><div style="--delay:0ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Advanced Developer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Jun 2012  Nov 2014 · 2 years 6 months</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="--delay:40ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="my-11 last:mb-0"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">Myone - Comunicação Multimédia</h3><p class="mb-3 text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">3 years 8 months</p><div class="relative ml-3"><span class="absolute top-3 bottom-0 -left-0.5 w-2 -translate-x-1/3 rounded bg-stone-300/60 dark:bg-white/5"></span><div class="space-y-4"><div style="--delay:0ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Multimedia Engineer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Oct 2008  May 2012 · 3 years 8 months</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="--delay:60.00000000000001ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="my-11 last:mb-0"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">Medula - Design de Comunicação</h3><p class="mb-3 text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">1 year 1 month</p><div class="relative ml-3"><span class="absolute top-3 bottom-0 -left-0.5 w-2 -translate-x-1/3 rounded bg-stone-300/60 dark:bg-white/5"></span><div class="space-y-4"><div style="--delay:0ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Web Designer | New Media Developer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Sep 2007  Sep 2008 · 1 year 1 month</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="--delay:80ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="my-11 last:mb-0"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">Freelance</h3><p class="mb-3 text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">3 years 8 months</p><div class="relative ml-3"><span class="absolute top-3 bottom-0 -left-0.5 w-2 -translate-x-1/3 rounded bg-stone-300/60 dark:bg-white/5"></span><div class="space-y-4"><div style="--delay:0ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down"><div class="relative pl-6"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-3 border-stone-400 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h4 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Freelance Web Developer/Designer</h4><p class="text-xs text-stone-500 dark:text-zinc-400">Jan 2004  Aug 2007 · 3 years 8 months</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="--delay:100ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down pt-12 text-sm italic">For more technical details and experience, please visit my <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulogoncalvs" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="underline">LinkedIn profile</a>.</p></div></section></main><footer><div class="border border-r-0 border-l-0 border-white/90